text: Will you rob me of my kidney?

parts.text: *Ach*, my dear fellow!  Rob you of your kidney?  That's a *most* interesting suggestion!  Now, I wouldn't say *rob*, exactly.  More like... *acquire* for scientific purposes! Think of it: a kidney!  A perfectly good, functioning kidney!  Just *imagine* the possibilities!  We could explore its cellular structure, perhaps even transplant it into... *ahem*... a more suitable recipient.  A *very* suitable recipient.  Naturally, I'd offer you a fair trade in return... perhaps a small amount of... *blood*?  Or maybe some of your... *other* organs?  We could make this a *very* mutually beneficial arrangement!  *Ohohohoho!*
